item.title: Things I've made so far
item.description: I can say how much I’ve read about web development or how many tutorials I’ve completed, but the real evidence will be things. Things I’ve made that work and that can go on my CV. So here’s where I’m at in terms of things. CS50x project(s) In my last blog I mentioned CS50x and why I stopped doing the course. Before that I did make some things, but sadly the course has its own IDE which doesn’t go on to Github, so I don’t have much to share.
